{"tid":1379995,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【六四2.0】習近平肯定六四鎮壓 高規格為李鵬送終 影射強硬立場對付香港局勢","createTime":"2019-07-29T02:00:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T06:00:52.000Z","uid":155095,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5c98f72ee81eb541b395942add0844af4003ddce","tid":1379995,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:00:38.000Z","msg":"source: <a href=\"https://www.worldjournal.com/6417906/article-肯定六四鎮壓-高規格送別李鵬-影射香港局勢？/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2F6417906%2Farticle-%E8%82%AF%E5%AE%9A%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B%E9%8E%AE%E5%A3%93-%E9%AB%98%E8%A6%8F%E6%A0%BC%E9%80%81%E5%88%A5%E6%9D%8E%E9%B5%AC-%E5%BD%B1%E5%B0%84%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%B1%80%E5%8B%A2%EF%BC%9F%2F&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyy5a0YVntLK4LebkCjpCDSOM%3D&h=6c138e28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldjournal.com/6417906/article-肯定六四鎮壓-高規格送別李鵬-影射香港局勢？/</a><br />\n<br />\n日前過世、被民運人士稱為「<span style=\"color: red;\">六四屠夫</span>」的<strong>中共前總理李鵬</strong>告別儀式北京時間29日上午在北京<span style=\"color: red;\">八寶山</span>革命公墓大禮堂舉行，預計中共政治局包括<strong>習近平</strong>在內現任<strong>七名常委</strong>將全數出席。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/zhuanlan/yehuazhongnanhai/gx-07262019133654.html/AP_11070113594.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2Fzhuanlan%2Fyehuazhongnanhai%2Fgx-07262019133654.html%2FAP_11070113594.jpg&h=127471e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大陸全國各地（包括<strong>港澳</strong>）都將<strong>降半旗</strong>誌哀。外媒稱，中共以<span style=\"color: red;\">最高規格</span>替李鵬送終，有影射將用<span style=\"color: red;\">強硬立場</span>對付當前<span style=\"color: red;\">香港局勢</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5d36e1a9da237719585583b5.jpg/iW_VJeoGkKuQMKMF909clBuqx59P4lh3m6qVXJuqlVw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5d36e1a9da237719585583b5.jpg%2FiW_VJeoGkKuQMKMF909clBuqx59P4lh3m6qVXJuqlVw&h=1acf5993&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n李鵬告別儀式將按照「<strong>正國級</strong>」最高規格，預料習近平、李克強等中共政治局常委將全部出席。新華社稱，今天北京天安門、新華門、人民大會堂、外交部，各省、自治區、直轄市黨委和政府所在地，<span style=\"color: red;\">香港特別行政區、澳門特別行政區</span>，各邊境口岸，對外海空港口，中共駐外使領館都將<span style=\"color: red;\">下半旗誌哀</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190726/_2019072623043449611.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190726%2F_2019072623043449611.jpg&h=931222e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n李鵬22日在北京逝世，終年91歲。官方形容李鵬是「中國共產黨的優秀黨員，久經考驗的忠誠的共產主義戰士，傑出的無產階級革命家、政治家，黨和國家的卓越領導人」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/23195046/pan.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F23195046%2Fpan.png&h=dc686e84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共以最高規格下葬李鵬，被外界視為中共力挺李鵬在「六四」事件中，採取強硬對付學運的立場，因其保衛了紅色江山。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/riaCaF6nKJE/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FriaCaF6nKJE%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=68ab4807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有評論認為，中共高度評價李鵬，也在影射當前香港局勢。美國之音引述中國大陸人權組織公民力量創辦人楊建利認為，中共給李鵬的訃告重提「政治動亂」和「反革命暴亂」，反映出中共意識到今年是高度安全隱患意識年，要防範所有的危險，包括香港正在進行的抗議活動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EAJ-qseUEAAQsJs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEAJ-qseUEAAQsJs.jpg&h=755cde69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n楊建利說，訃告代表「把六四的定性死死地放在一個地方，告訴大家，不要有其他想法，這是我們的定性，今年的安全是第一要務」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/1838/1*09ODKRu6cFSoaA2OGjGmeQ.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmiro.medium.com%2Fmax%2F1838%2F1%2A09ODKRu6cFSoaA2OGjGmeQ.jpeg&h=863ba2a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n報導也引述政論作家陳破空表示，訃告中提到李鵬「平息反革命暴亂」顯然影射當下香港局勢。因為過了幾天後，中共國防部發言人就聲稱，根據中共香港特別行政區「駐軍法」，只要港府需要，就可以派解放軍維持秩序。"},{"pid":"e973c64c2cbb3a7e88c0d6fd1061b493a05af6b4","tid":1379995,"uid":155095,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:30:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">請勿帶包</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://botanwang.com/sites/default/files/images/EAh81GFUIAA-L2v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbotanwang.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fimages%2FEAh81GFUIAA-L2v.jpg&h=8d1d0247&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"96f51b72b6af70d2251a2e6eff8947a34915816c","tid":1379995,"uid":155095,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:00:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1*PbV4992MhW7EKngXHgHV9A.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmiro.medium.com%2Fmax%2F1400%2F1%2APbV4992MhW7EKngXHgHV9A.jpeg&h=adf0dea7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"334eba37c8ce82d0ab939944a224f60b4f0e9f26","tid":1379995,"uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:23:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50aae9b10f8b49f913255c727234752346d318f7","tid":1379995,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"334eba37c8ce82d0ab939944a224f60b4f0e9f26","tid":1379995,"uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:23:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:00:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"116c90a430141414c2e447fa4145e737c6f45d0a","tid":1379995,"uid":161341,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:07:05.000Z","msg":"要求解放軍武力鎮壓香港，並出兵攻打外國勢力。"},{"pid":"239fdee39d33ede71ab9caed866c531255156b23","tid":1379995,"uid":158090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:09:09.000Z","msg":"郭家麒: 暴力既源頭係林鄭政府，造成今日既亂局係有中央政府包庇林鄭同警隊 | LIHKG<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1380805/page/1\" dat